<lyrics>[V1]
 Na velchum ah thli a hran ca, Lawng a pil dengmang, Thli nih a hranh i
 a rawk deng, A thuk ti chungah.

[C1]
   Khamhbawi kha zoh u law, nan hnangam tuah u, &quot;Khuadei tiang kan umpi
   hna lai, Kan khamh lai, tih hlah u,&quot; a ti; Asi, kan khamh hna lai, tiah a
   ti, Khuadei tiang kan umpi hna lai. (pi hna lai)

[V2]
 Ruahchannak a dihmi hna kha, Lawng cungah an um, Bawipa auhnak aw an
 theih in, An lung aa lawm than,

[C2]
   Khamhbawi kha zoh u law, nan hnangam tuah u, &quot;Khuadei tiang kan umpi
   hna lai, Kan khamh lai, tih hlah u,&quot; a ti; Asi, kan khamh hna lai, tiah a
   ti, Khuadei tiang kan umpi hna lai. (pi hna lai)

[V3]
 Tilet cung thlichia a hran lio ah, Lawng a pil dengmang, Khamh awkah
 Jesuh a kal i, Phannak a dai cang.

[C3]
   Khamhbawi kha zoh u law, nan hnangam tuah u, &quot;Khuadei tiang kan umpi
   hna lai, Kan khamh lai, tih hlah u,&quot; a ti; Asi, kan khamh hna lai, tiah a
   ti, Khuadei tiang kan umpi hna lai. (pi hna lai)

[V4]
 Nannih dawtnak ca a tum i, Nang ca'h a thi cang; A tha lo hlaw in va
 zum tuah, Inn tha na phak lai.

[C4]
   Khamhbawi kha zoh u law, nan hnangam tuah u, &quot;Khuadei tiang kan umpi
   hna lai, Kan khamh lai, tih hlah u,&quot; a ti; Asi, kan khamh hna lai, tiah a
   ti, Khuadei tiang kan umpi hna lai. (pi hna lai)</lyrics>
